ARM: EXYNOS4: Use generic DMA PL330 driver

This patch makes Samsung EXYNOS4 to use DMA PL330 driver
on DMADEVICE. The EXYNOS4 uses DMA generic APIs instead of
SAMSUNG specific S3C-PL330 APIs.

